Detailed Description

Parameters:
profileType 
  • Identifies the type of profile 0x00 = 3GPP
profileIndex 
  • Index of profile whose settings were loaded prior to session parameter negotiation for the current call. If this TLV is not present, data call parameters are based on device default settings for each parameter
